</a></span></section>\r\n			</section>\r\n		</section>\r\n	</section>\r\n</section>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<section class=\"yead_editor\" id=\"1_48\" label=\"Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved.\" onmousedown=\"shifuMouseDown(\'1_48\')\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';margin: 5px auto;white-space: normal;\">\r\n	<p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;padding:0;height:32px;line-height:18px;font-weight:400;border-bottom-color:#e3e3e3;border-bottom-width:1px;border-bottom-style:solid;white-space:normal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\"><span class=\"yead_bdbc yead_color\" style=\"padding: 0px 2px 3px; color: rgb(0, 88, 156); line-height: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 88, 156); border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; float: left; display: block;text-indent: 0em;\">1、低层建筑产品</span></span></p>\r\n</section>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"revealfootp\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 宋体, HELVETICA; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; white-space: normal;\">\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">采用0.6至3.3mm厚的热镀锌钢板,混轧成截面为C型和U型钢骨，通过&ldquo;工厂化&rdquo;规模生产，组成复合式墙板、楼板、屋架等构件，在现场进行快速组装,干作业施工。</span></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">适用于3层及以下建筑体。如：住宅别墅、绿色小镇、旅游度假、养老养生建筑等。</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"revealimg\" style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 宋体, HELVETICA; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; white-space: normal;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://182.50.112.199:8081/userfiles/1/images/cms/article/2015/12/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20151217001159.png\" style=\"width: 650px; height: 418px;\" /></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"revealimg\" style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 宋体, HELVETICA; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; white-space: normal;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\"><a name=\"hig\"></a></span></p>\r\n<section class=\"yead_editor\" id=\"1_48\" label=\"Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved.\" onmousedown=\"shifuMouseDown(\'1_48\')\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';margin: 5px auto;white-space: normal;\">\r\n	<p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;padding:0;height:32px;line-height:18px;font-weight:400;border-bottom-color:#e3e3e3;border-bottom-width:1px;border-bottom-style:solid;white-space:normal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\"><span class=\"yead_bdbc yead_color\" style=\"padding: 0px 2px 3px; color: rgb(0, 88, 156); line-height: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 88, 156); border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; float: left; display: block;text-indent: 0em;\">2、多层建筑产品</span></span></p>\r\n</section>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"revealfootp\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 宋体, HELVETICA; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; white-space: normal;\">\r\n	<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">主体结构为钢框架,采用钢骨结构作为其维护结构。该体系融合了各自优势，进一步提高了钢框架本身的抗震、防风性能。 适用于6层以下中小型建筑体。如：住宅、公寓、酒店、会所、游泳馆、办公用房、医院、学校、旅游度假配套设施等。</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"revealimg\" style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 宋体, HELVETICA; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; white-space: normal;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://182.50.112.199:8081/userfiles/1/images/cms/article/2015/12/%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%E5%9B%BE(1).jpg\" style=\"width: 677px; height: 521px;\" /></span></div>', '', '', '1');
